; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/spinningsword.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Vasilissa</span><br>  Posts: 143<br> <font color=#993300>(12/4/00 11:43:15 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://facelink.com/Hippolyte?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Watches and willing to help out</span><hr size=1> :::Hipp senses the pup near her feet and smiles.  She watches him as he lays down and watches the young warriors practice inside the pavilion. The kneeling down she gently runs a hand over his head and down the back of his neck::: hey Skye ::she smiled and kept her hand on him..watching the practice a little bit longer then stood up and turned to go over to the kitchen hut and find something to eat.  She stops and looks to Skye:: you hungry boy? Let's find something ::she waves him to come on and turns back to the hut::  <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>
